definition: Yueyang prefecture level city in Hunan

sentences.english: Xiong Linbo was named one of the ten eminent doctors in Yueyang City in 2008
sentences.chinese: 熊林波2008年被評爲岳陽市首界十大名醫。

sentences.english: Zou Guojun were named outstanding experts of Yueyang City.
sentences.chinese: 鄒國軍等爲岳陽市優秀專家。

sentences.english: In recent years, Yueyang city high-tech industries developed rapidly.
sentences.chinese: 近年來，岳陽市高新技術產業發展較快。

sentences.english: The article summed up the experience of library of Yueyang Agricultural school serving teaching.
sentences.chinese: 文章總結了岳陽市農校圖書室爲教學服務的三點經驗。

sentences.english: This afternoon, the torch will head to Miluo, 110 kilometers from Yueyang.
sentences.chinese: 下午，火炬將前往汨羅市，離岳陽市有110千里遠。

sentences.english: Now the hospital has 976 staff members.
sentences.chinese: 岳陽市中醫院現在幹部職工976人。
